Package org.opensextant.giscore.filegdb

Class Geodatabase

java.lang.Object
org.opensextant.giscore.filegdb.GDB
org.opensextant.giscore.filegdb.Geodatabase
public class Geodatabase extends GDB
Wraps the FileGDB API Geodatabase Object and presents the needed operations on the Geodatabase Object so they can be executed from Java.
